Package jetbrains.exodus

Class FileByteIterable

  • java.lang.Object
    • jetbrains.exodus.FileByteIterable
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<ByteIterable>, ByteIterable
    public class FileByteIterable
extends java.lang.Object
implements ByteIterable
    An adapter to the contents of a region of a file. Doesn't support getBytesUnsafe() as it unconditionally throws UnsupportedOperationException.

    Avoid using this class with Android API level less than 26.
